نJulia Hinchcliffe 1975-2010
"I thought of you today but that is nothing new.
I thought of you yesterday and days before that too.
I think of you in silence, I often speak your name.
Your Laughter fills the sunlight and echoes through the rain.
Your memory is a keepsake from which we'll never part
God has you in his keeping, I have you in my heart.""ي
êKhadija Diana May Cohen nأ©e Greenstreet
b 23rd February 1933, Camden Town, d 20th July 1999 in Spain
Resident of Tavistock Court,
Graduate of the School of Oriental & African Studies.
Beloved wife, mother, grandmother and friend."ٍ
